title: Trump, Abe meet amid 'extremely high level' talks with North Korea
text:
Trump, Abe meet amid 'extremely high level' talks with North Korea Tuesday, April 17, 2018 - 02:14 
Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe is set to meet U.S. President Donald Trump in Mar-a-Lago, Florida, where North Korea is expected to dominate talks. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
